<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.10.1">
<l>tirumaṭantai maṇmaṭantai yirupālun tikaḻat tīviṉaikaḷ pōyakala vaṭiyavarkaṭ keṉṟum</l>
<l>aruḷnaṭantiv vēḻulakat tavarppaṇiya vāṉō ramarntētta viruntaviṭam perumpukaḻvē tiyarvāḻ</l>
<l>tarumiṭaṅkaḷ malarkaḷmiku kaitaikaḷceṅ kaḻunīr tāmaraikaḷ taṭaṅkaṭoṟu miṭaṅkaṭoṟum tikaḻa</l>
<l>aruviṭaṅkaḷ poḻiltaḻuvi yeḻiltikaḻu nāṅkū rarimēya viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Arimēya Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr where the beauty</l>
<l rend="indent">of [its] rare places encircled by gardens shines,</l>
<l>As screw pine with many blossoms, red waterlilies, and lotuses shine</l>
<l rend="indent">in every pool and every place, places where Vedic experts</l>
<l rend="indent">of great fame naturally live,</l>
<l>The place where [he] sits as celestials praise and long for [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">as lady Tiru and lady earth shine on either side,</l>
<l>[And] as people of the seven worlds worship,</l>
<l rend="indent">always dispersing grace to devotees so that [their] evil deeds vanish.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
